cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CE 

The paper discusses the performance and execution modes of machine learning frameworks, specifically in the context of supervised learning. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of deep learning (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques, as well as the impact of hardware allocation and placement (cs.CE).
